                <mxCell id="desc2" value="① WindowMotorECU (LIN Slave 0x21): Motor 동작 중 10ms 주기로 Motor_Current 값을 BCM에 보고&#10;② BCM (LIN Master): Motor_Current &gt; 50A 감지 → DTC B1234 생성 → BCM_FaultStatus(0x500) CAN-LS 전송 + Motor_Stop 명령 (LIN Control)&#10;③ CGW 라우팅: CAN-LS 0x500 → CAN-HS → Cluster RED 경고등 점등 (FTTI &lt; 50ms)&#10;④ Tester: UDS 0x10 0x03 (Extended Session) → 0x19 0x02 (Read DTC) → 0x14 (Clear DTC) → OTA 0x34/0x36×N/0x37" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#cccccc;fillColor=#f9f9f9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;fontSize=10;rounded=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="432" width="760" height="68" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
            </root>
        </mxGraphModel>
